SummaryEnglish: The Earth is in danger of surviving after being attacked by the mysterious force "Ulgaru" who claims to be a pan-galaxy unified empire. Team Rabbits of children born to fight by genetic engineering, Izuru, Asagi, Kay, Tamaki, Suruga, and Anju will challenge the battle with the device "AHSMB".
Aliases: Gekijouban Majesutikku purinsu: Kakusei no idenshi
